metadata.name: Somewhere in the mountains
metadata.description: I looked out the window and saw the sun was setting down. Itâ€™s rays were bright red and passed through the branches of trees. My faithful friend named Oscar looked at me with his big eyes and I told him that we are going for a walk. Climbing a mountain near my house, I saw the beauty of the sunset. Oscar once again gave me an incredible memory that I captured with my camera.
